{"tid":84394,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國產「尿袋」爆炸傷人","createTime":"2017-01-17T13:20:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-17T23:47:29.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6d23ef8bbaad31abd1ccbabf1cb6762ca0a1e6db","tid":84394,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T13:20:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170117/19899483\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170117%2F19899483&d=bhgyCO6mn7isTI%2FN8FzTogT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=457155e4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170117%2F19899483&h=4b2f17dd\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170117/19899483</a><br />\n<br />\n國產「尿袋」爆炸傷人<br />\n<br />\n12,205<br />\nInitial ImagePlay Button Image<br />\n適中字型<br />\n較大字型<br />\n<br />\n ■爆炸「尿袋」外殼爆開，電池燒至焦黑，下圖為同牌子尿袋。劉永明攝<br />\n■爆炸「尿袋」外殼爆開，電池燒至焦黑，下圖為同牌子尿袋。劉永明攝<br />\n【本報訊】「尿袋」又出事，將軍澳明德邨一名男子，昨午替手機流動充電器充電期間突冒煙起火，兩度發出爆炸聲，事主慌忙將火撲救，輕微燒傷手腳。<br />\n姓陳事主本身為結他導師，昨午2時許，他將尿袋插在房間拖板充電，洗完澡吹頭期間，突聽到怪聲，「好似放煙花咁嘅聲」，循聲赫見尿袋爆炸冒煙，他連忙將尿袋丟落地。<br />\n<br />\n「十幾個打火機咁大火」<br />\n尿袋火花夾雜嗆臭煙霧不斷冒出，他用濕布包住丟入廁所，之後再傳出兩聲爆炸，火花四濺，當尿袋沒再冒煙，他揭開濕布，赫見尿袋如同黑炭，外殼爆開露出數個焦黑電池，廁所地板牆身熏黑，爆炸「十幾個打火機咁大火！」他致電報警，消防及警方接報到場，曾檢視尿袋會否再有爆炸風險，經10分鐘確保安全後離去。<br />\n陳稱，尿袋名為PRODA Power Box，購入約一年，電量為20,000mAh，一直運作正常，他一星期大約充電一次，今次充電約半小時。他檢視過尿袋是香港設計、內地牌子製造。<br />\n■記者劉永明  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n經紀捱斬女民安隊員施救<br />\n下一則<br />\n九巴荃灣路　直撼吊臂車"},{"pid":"a42b77a601a7812835168c8931252900e3728095","tid":84394,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T13:22:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/video/20170117/org/1484594616_bfaf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fvideo%2F20170117%2Forg%2F1484594616_bfaf.jpg&h=2c7fa1dd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2bfb735c66b42a14a843da77e46bb5ea0adffcf4","tid":84394,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T13:29:29.000Z","msg":"符合蝗情"},{"pid":"65d98d34f5ab3f6ac0b745200a2b8e7a89beb5ce","tid":84394,"uid":3773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T13:32:46.000Z","msg":"炸炸~炸你老母閪呀"},{"pid":"26be22c4d88db28c24c266f21c62fba516bfecdb","tid":84394,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T13:37:41.000Z","msg":"唔爆至奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f1e644b61d5b4cec3de4ac88b283961f7d9f732","tid":84394,"uid":60113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T13:44:24.000Z","msg":"炸到一屋都係尿"},{"pid":"a02c8fa4c83c6cd3097190872cb2d7b26df49a23","tid":84394,"uid":27133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T15:38:52.000Z","msg":"香港牌子？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3da7a8e84c9ad2347d177c7df47b757836ee3c1a","tid":84394,"uid":13149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T16:54:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">他將尿袋插在房間拖板充電</span><br />\n拖板個usb都夠膽用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"509ce176c8bd5a4a6bca6b9aa5a438fe4695503c","tid":84394,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T17:02:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/video/20170117/org/1484594616_bfaf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fvideo%2F20170117%2Forg%2F1484594616_bfaf.jpg&h=2c7fa1dd&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n條mk 好似代言人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a06a593b9977a43b7d27ed45d11bd05104e1eb9a","tid":84394,"uid":32706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s